Cloud Deployment 
I USED HEROKU CLOUD AND USED THESE STEPS :
INSTALL THE PACKAGE BY USING COMMAND - pip install gunicorn
INSTALL THE GIT REPOSITARY - git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
CREATE A TEXT FILE - pip freeze > requirements.txt
CREATE PROCFILE - web: gunicorn your_app_name:app
LOGIN TO HEROKU 
CREAKE A HEROKU-heroku create 
 
DEPLOY HEROKU APP 
AND THEN LOGIN 
